dc_title_s: Tbilisi city map 2015 : detailed map of the downtown. Tbilisi and surroundings
dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights on "Surroundings" map. City-center street map shows buildings, generalized land use, locations of services, and points of interest. Ancillary map on recto: [Tbilisi Metro rapid transit system, including line under construction]. Inset map on verso: Administrative map of Georgia. "© Geoland 2014." At foot of panel title: www.geoland.ge
